Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Agent Core Module - Production Grade

Provides comprehensive agent identity, lifecycle management, and core capabilities for AI-to-AI communication.
Essential for autonomous agent systems with robust identity management, state tracking, and lifecycle operations.

Advanced features include:
- Agent identity and metadata management with cryptographic verification
- Lifecycle state transitions with validation and rollback capabilities
- Skill and capability registration with dependency resolution
- Agent discovery and registry integration with load balancing
- State persistence and recovery with checkpointing
- Performance monitoring and metrics with real-time optimization
- Security and permission management with sandboxing
- Runtime execution engine with async support and error recovery
- Circuit breaker patterns and graceful degradation
- Distributed coordination and consensus mechanisms
:End Note

